btw. as a hint, if u stand in the same place where u started to cast the spell, even if u run miles while casting, spell does not interrupt, since they just store the position when u start casting and compare them to the position where u are when spell should go off.<br>
<br>
as for the ac, i can tell it helps nothing.<br>
even if u get hit for 0 dmg, and this happens u can get an interrupt.<br>
only channeling focus and aa where u avoid the hits completely help.<br>
